"\n"
"To construct regional and global level estimates, when survey-based "
"estimates are not available for the reference years of 2000, 2005 or 2010 "
"all survey-based estimates within a 5 year window of the reference year are "
"“lined-up” by using a combination of interpolation, extrapolation, "
"econometric modelling and imputation based on regional medians ( Wagstaff "
